Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.50,0:23:10.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}そのために強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:16.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}愛するもの  笑う未来を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.01,0:23:21.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}あいつの梦を声を守るため
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:23.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}泣いたあいつの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.76,0:23:26.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}涙を止める
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.27,0:23:31.27,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}それ以外理由は要らない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:21.79,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}這雙手能抓住的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.08,0:22:26.87,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}這雙手能傷害的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.29,0:22:31.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}如果只是哀嘆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:36.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}這雙手從開始就無法守護住任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:40.55,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}獸矛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:43.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:47.23,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)}我是否在向前看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.78,0:22:55.24,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}爲了心愛的人  生存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.24,0:23:00.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}爲了守護那個傢伙的今天和明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:02.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(200,200)\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&}哭泣的那傢伙
